article.description: — Asbjorn Midtgaard registered 16 points and nine rebounds as Grand Canyon romped past Dixie State 81-46 on Saturday night.
article.headline: Midtgaard carries Grand Canyon over Dixie State 81-46
article.linkText: Midtgaard carries Grand Canyon over Dixie State 81-46
article.story: ST. GEORGE, Utah -- — Asbjorn Midtgaard registered 16 points and nine rebounds as Grand Canyon romped past Dixie State 81-46 on Saturday night. Alessandro Lever had 13 points for Grand Canyon (10-3, 4-0 Western Athletic Conference), which earned its sixth straight victory. Chance McMillian added 11 points. Jovan Blacksher Jr. had 10 points. Dixie State scored 22 points in the first half, a season low for the team. Cameron Gooden had 14 points for the Trailblazers (4-7, 0-4), who have now lost six consecutive games. The Antelopes improve to 2-0 against the Trailblazers for the season. Grand Canyon defeated Dixie State 77-74 on Friday. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
